data.description: Welcome to your new home in Spartanburg County School District 2! This charming and cozy three-bedroom home is situated on a large lot, providing plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or just enjoying the fresh air. The serene and rural location offers a tranquil atmosphere while being just a stone's throw away from shopping centers, dining options, schools, and hospitals, making it the perfect combination of convenience and comfort. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living space. The three cozy bedrooms offer plenty of space for rest and relaxation, while the two full bathrooms provide added convenience. Outside, the expansive yard is perfect for outdoor activities, barbecues, and entertaining. The driveway provides plenty of parking space and the shed conveys offering additional storage space. With its convenient location and sidewalk, this lovely home is a short walk from Boiling Springs High, Boiling Springs Freshman Academy, dining, shopping and medical. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours!
